Well, now in the mention of Terumi and BlazBlue, I may as well ask this to Riot...

Has BlazBlue itself been used as an inspiration for something in the League of Legends? Well, you said that {{champion:92}} draws inspiration from fighting games and their combos, but I thought it is more from either general fighting games or Super Smash Bros. The only link to BlazBlue is just something as her voice (Cristina Vee, AKA Noel. Only mentioned this because despite Patrick Seitz (Ragna) is involved voicing {{champion:236}} {{champion:58}} {{champion:96}}, they are not having fighting game influences), so I don't think you had BB in mind when it comes to designing {{champion:92}}

Just for fun, if you are going to take a BlazBlue character as an inspiration for a new champion, who would you pick, Riot? Just one.
